    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a large piece of<strong> tin foil </strong>(or two!) and lay your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>and<strong> green beans </strong>in the middle</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and scrunch the edges up to form a tightly sealed parcel[s],  then put the parcel[s] on a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
