        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and cook for 6-7 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
