        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spicy hoisin meat-free mince</strong> with the<strong> sesame greens</strong> and <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> reserved chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
